#: _versions/main/guides/security-cors.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Cross-Origin Resource Sharing (CORS)"
msgstr "跨源资源共享（CORS）"

#: _versions/main/guides/security-cors.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Enable and configure CORS in Quarkus to specify allowed origins, methods, "
"and headers, guiding browsers in handling cross-origin requests safely."
msgstr "在 Quarkus 中启用和配置 CORS，指定允许的来源、方法和标题，指导浏览器安全处理跨来源请求。"

#: _versions/main/guides/security-cors.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Cross-Origin Resource Sharing (CORS) uses HTTP headers to manage browser "
"requests for resources from external origins securely.\n"
"By specifying permitted origins, methods, and headers, Quarkus servers can "
"use the CORS filter to enable browsers to request resources across domains "
"while maintaining controlled access.\n"
"This mechanism enhances security and supports legitimate cross-origin "
"requests.\n"
"For more on origin definitions, see the link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/"
"doc/html/rfc6454[Web Origin Concept]."
msgstr ""
"跨源资源共享（CORS）使用 HTTP 标头安全地管理浏览器对外部资源的请求。通过指定允许的来源、方法和标头，Quarkus 服务器可以使用 CORS "
"过滤器，使浏览器能够跨域请求资源，同时保持受控访问。这种机制增强了安全性，并支持合法的跨源请求。有关起源定义的更多信息，请参阅 link:https://"
"datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc6454[网络起源概念] 。"

#: _versions/main/guides/security-cors.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enabling the CORS filter"
msgstr "启用 CORS 过滤器"

#: _versions/main/guides/security-cors.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To enforce CORS policies in your application, enable the Quarkus CORS filter "
"by adding the following line to the `src/main/resources/application."
"properties` file:"
msgstr ""
"要在应用程序中执行 CORS 策略，请在 `src/main/resources/application.properties` "
"文件中添加以下一行，启用 Quarkus CORS 过滤器："

#: _versions/main/guides/security-cors.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The filter intercepts all incoming HTTP requests to identify cross-origin "
"requests and applies the configured policy.\n"
"The filter then adds CORS headers to the HTTP response, informing browsers "
"about allowed origins and access parameters.\n"
"For preflight requests, the filter returns an HTTP response immediately.\n"
"For regular CORS requests, the filter denies access with an HTTP 403 status "
"if the request violates the configured policy; otherwise, the filter "
"forwards the request to the destination if the policy allows it."
msgstr ""
"该过滤器拦截所有传入的 HTTP 请求，以识别跨源请求并应用配置的策略。然后，过滤器会在 HTTP 响应中添加 CORS "
"标头，告知浏览器允许的来源和访问参数。对于预检请求，过滤器会立即返回 HTTP 响应。对于常规 CORS 请求，如果请求违反了配置策略，过滤器会以 "
"HTTP 403 状态拒绝访问；否则，如果策略允许，过滤器会将请求转发到目的地。"

